---
title: Korean-Style Beef Stir Fry with Broccolini, Brown Rice, and Sesame
description: Stir-fries are an unbeatable weeknight dinner – simple, fast, and delicious. This beef is marinated with intensely aromatic ingredients for incredible results. If you have time, let it marinate in the fridge for up to an hour to marry the flavours!
